 It's like some inkling of some deep truth.

41:40.960 --> 41:43.280
 Like what do you think that would actually look like?

41:43.280 --> 41:45.200
 Would it be an experimental result?

41:46.480 --> 41:48.920
 I mean, it will have to have some kind of experimental

