 or imagination on top of it

1:04:45.200 --> 1:04:47.280
 that kind of scrambles that a little bit more

1:04:47.280 --> 1:04:49.680
 and like has access to...

1:04:49.680 --> 1:04:51.800
 I don't know, it's kind of...

