 And part of the reason is,

1:06:25.960 --> 1:06:27.600
 I think I've talked a little bit already

1:06:27.600 --> 1:06:29.280
 about these holes in physics,

1:06:29.280 --> 1:06:32.840
 like the theories we have in physics,

